        "content": "### Business Summary\n**Doctors ki Sales Performance**: Hamare pass jo doctors hain, unme sab se zyada sales generate karne wala **Product 3** hai, jiske total sales **PKR 11,073,300.00** hain.\n\n### Current vs Predicted Sales\n* **Current Sales**: PKR 11,073,300.00\n* **Predicted Sales (15% growth, 2x visit increase)**: \n  * 2x visit increase ke case me, sales **PKR 12,684,178.50** tak pohnch sakti hain (assuming 15% growth)\n  * Ya **PKR 13,293,103.50** tak bhi pohnch sakti hain (assuming 20% growth)\n\n### Strategic Recommendation\nHamare doctors ko **Product 3** ke sales me aur focus karna chahiye, ta ke hum apne sales targets ko achieve kar sakein aur market me apni position mazboot bana sakein.",
        "sql": "SELECT \n  product_name, \n  SUM(total_amount) AS \"Total Sales\"\nFROM master_sale \nWHERE customer_type = 'Doctors'\nGROUP BY 1\nORDER BY 2 DESC\nLIMIT 1;",
